text: A word of caution: 80-20% principle is a hoax in medicine and engineering. Imagine learning only 20% of the civil engineering syllabus and making a simple full-scale life size house. The house is likely to have cracks, leakages, electrical wiring issues, fire-safety issues etc. One also needs to be sensible enough to figure out when and where to apply what principle.
